corduroy road
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number: 1
Definition:a primitive road made of logs placed side by side at right angles to traffic [often made of manuka].
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
Region:[none]
